2. Startups
Startups ek alag career path hain compared to corporate jobs:
Pros
Fast learning curve — ek insaan multiple roles handle karta hai
Zyada ownership aur direct impact dikhta hai
Equity/ESOPs ka chance (agar company grow kare to bada return)
Networking aur exposure jaldi milta hai
Cons
Job security kam hoti hai (funding pe depend karta hai)
Salary starting mein kam ho sakti hai bade companies ke comparison mein
Work-life balance challenging ho sakta hai (long hours common hain)
Types of roles in startups
Founding Engineer
Early-stage SDE (jaldi joining, high responsibility)
Growth/Product roles 
